confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>Cancel all lines on the account, including vol suspended lines</li>
<li><span>Customer is billed any outstanding balance until cancelation date=
 (prorate)</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">If there is no IP or ILS loan ba=
lance is zero for the device associated with the line/CTN, the line cancela=
tion flow is BAU</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">If CIPID in passed, ODS includes=
 it in the BSSe-OC request for cease line</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">BSSe-OC includes CIPID in the PO=
 published to OCE</span></li>
<li>OCE calls ILS to check if there is active loan for the device associate=
d with the line being canceled</li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">OCE calls ILS to accelerate the =
loan with non-payment reason code. ILS eventually closes the loan when cust=
omer pays the loan balance. ILS probably gets an update from CFM/RTB on the=
 payment.</span></li>
<li>ILS API for acceleration - /servicing/manualacceleration</li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
