confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>ACC need to send the relevant reason code in cancelation request</li>
<li>If device has no IP, its going to be BAU cancel line flow. It could be =
future dated cancelation to match the deployment date.&nbsp;</li>
<li>We need to hold the CTN for certain period of time before letting it go=
 thru the aging process and eventually make it available in the general poo=
l.=20
<ol>
<li>When OCE calls TLG-NM to release the number, need to specify the milita=
ry hold.&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">Need to hash out this AP=
I details with NM.&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol></li>
<li>If device has IP and loan was created before deployment date, OCE need =
to call ILS to cancel the line with specific reason code to write-off the l=
oan.<span>&nbsp;</span></li>
<li>If loan was created after deployment, the device is expected to be retu=
rned. So, it follows BRE flow but outside of the BRE window.</li>
<li>&nbsp;Refer to References section for additional military use cases</li=
>
</ol></td>
