Description</th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" colspan=3D"5" class=3D"=
confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>ACC calls BUPS (PaymentMs) to accelerate the ILS loan</li>
<li>BUPS calls ILS to accelerate the loan</li>
<li>Acceleration itself doesn't close the loan. It just adds the loan balan=
ce to next bill via RTB</li>
<li>The loan is actually closed when the customer pays the bill, and CFM up=
dates the same to ILS</li>
<li>ILS generates loan closure event when the loan is closed.&nbsp;</li>
<li>ODS listens to ILS loan closure event and creates an order to remove fe=
atures such as NUA and any associated promos since acceleration requires re=
moving these features/promos</li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">ODS submits feature/promo remova=
l order to BSSe-OC</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">BSSe-OC publishes PO to OG/OCE</=
span></li>
<li>While executing the order, OCE interfaces with ILS to remove NUA and as=
sociated promos, if applicable</li>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">OCE calls BSSe-OC to update the =
PI to expire NUA and device promos. as applicable</span></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
