<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Prorated MRC shall be given if line terminati=
on is done mid-cycle</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Loan cancelation happens on future date, unti=
l then customer is billed BAU</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Current date or back date with same bill cycl=
e</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Yes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Cancel service on order date</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Write-off loan on deployment date</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Disconnect from network or order submit date<=
/p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Prorated MRC shall be given if line terminati=
on is done mid-cycle</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Loan will be written off and service will be =
canceled.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Current/Back date</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>No</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Suspend service on order date</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>No change to loan</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Suspend from network on order submit date</p>=
</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">Can we c=
ontinue charging and then do credit?</span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li><strong>Doc approved:</strong> ACC shall send a new separate order to c=
ancel service with Military reason. (Same as #2)</li>
<li><strong>Doc rejected or doc not uploaded in given time:</strong> ACC sh=
all send a new separate order to resume from suspend.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Future Date</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>No</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Start suspending service on deployment date: =
Suspend service order future dated</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>No change to loan</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Suspend on the deployment (future) date</p></=
td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">Can we c=
ontinue charging and then do credit?</span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Order =
submit date: Mar 1 (Future suspend date: Mar 5)</span></p><p>Deployment Dat=
e: Mar 5 (Suspend service on Mar 5)</p><p>Last date to verify doc: Mar 15</=
p><p><br></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Doc approved on Mar 3 (before deployment date):</strong> ACC wi=
ll send future cancel service on Mar 3 (covered in #1) and ACC will send an=
other order to cancel future dated suspend service. On Mar 5, service will =
get canceled.</li>
<li><strong>Doc approved on Mar 6 (after deployment date):</strong> ACC wil=
l send cancel service order on Mar 6 (covered in #2)</li>
<li><strong>Doc rejected on Mar 3 (before deployment date):</strong> ACC wi=
ll send cancel future dated suspend service order.</li>
<li><strong>Doc rejected on Mar 6 (after deployment date) or doc not upload=
ed in given time:</strong> ACC will send resume from suspend service order =
on Mar 6 because service would have got suspended on Mar 5.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout single" data-layout=3D"single">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<hr>
<p style=3D"text-align: center;"><strong>AT&amp;T Proprietary (Restricted)<=
/strong></p>
<p>Only for use by authorized individuals or designated team(s) within the =
AT&amp;T companies and not for general distribution.</p>
